title: "SaFE-Scale: scaling up safety evaluation of large language models on radiology multiple-choice questions"
abstract: >
  Code release for the SaFE-Scale paper.  Reproduces the full evaluation
  pipeline (RAG context construction, multi-condition LLM inference,
  LLM-judge answer verification, bootstrap statistical analysis,
  supplementary tables/figures) on the RadSaFE-200 dataset.
